    <sidebar xml:id="ceilo_intro"><para>The Helion OpenStack Metering service is based on the OpenStack Ceilometer API. The Helion
        metering service collects and provides access to OpenStack usage data that can be used for
        billing reporting such as showback, and chargeback. The metering service can also provide
        general usage reporting. </para>
